Hearing.paragraph:
We know the threats that computing devices and systems face, which 
are almost too numerous to count:
  <bullet> Bot-nets;
  <bullet> Ransom-ware;
  <bullet> Zero Day Events;
  <bullet> Mal-ware;
  <bullet> Denial of Service Attacks;
  <bullet> Distributed Denial-of-Service Attacks;
  <bullet> Pharming;
  <bullet> Phishing;
  <bullet> Data Theft;
  <bullet> Data Breaches;
  <bullet> SQL Injection;
  <bullet> Man-in-the-middle attack.
